        "TileImage": "$($repository 0537209e-960f-4686-a9b4-65fe67bee060).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.\r\rYour targets, Orwell Newton and Roxana Franklin are an influencer power couple and command a large audience of fans over various social media platforms. They have leveraged their minor success to goad the Himmapan Hotel to allow them to rack up incessant room service bills, shout at staff and harass fellow hotel guests with loud music at night.\r\rNow, our client, Mrs Mookjai, the manager of the hotel, wants you to help conjure up an unforgettable check out experience for them.",
